OL,5, Security guards at Brixton Academy     
OL,6, regularly took bribes to let people in 
OL,7, without tickets, a whistleblower has   
OL,8, told the BBC.                          
OL,10,FTwo people lost their lives at the     
OL,11,Fsouth London venue in December, in a   
OL,12,Fcrush outside a gig by Afro-pop star   
OL,13,FAsake.                                 
OL,15,FA security guard has told File on Four 
OL,16,Fthat some members of his team would    
OL,17,Feach allow "a couple of hundred" extra 
OL,18,Fpeople into venues in exchange for     
OL,19,Fmoney. Their employer, AP Security, has
OL,20,Fdeclined to comment.                   
